node.text: Before we wrap up one of the wildest years, we’re taking a look back at our favorite @stockxteam highlights. Through it all, the crew shattered records, launched campaigns, supported important causes, partnered with insanely talented collaborators, AND hit $2.8 billy - all thanks to YOU. 2021, we’re ready for ya 😤

node.text:
The perfect pair for late summer rounds. Tap fast to secure an early release of the brand new @malbongolf x @newbalance 997G, exclusively via DropX. 

Inspired by the iconic caddie uniforms of The Masters, these shoes come correct in a crisp all white colorway with a pop of green trim. The gum sole gives a nice nod to OG sneaker culture, and the Cush+ insole offers premium comfort for playing any course. Plus, each pair includes a limited golf towel featuring StockX and Malbon Golf co-branding. 

Only 250 pairs are up for grabs. Link in bio for more.
